{"type":"message","id":"36b6500b","parentId":"9ed22b5a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:38:00.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"你好\"，这是一个简单的问候。让我先检查一下是否需要读取相关的记忆文件。\n\n根据 AGENTS.md 的指示：\n1. 如果是 MAIN SESSION（直接与人类对话），需要读取：\n   - SOUL.md - 已经在 Project Context 中加载了\n   - USER.md - 已经在 Project Context 中加载了\n   - memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (今天 + 昨天)\n   - MEMORY.md\n\n当前上下文显示：\n- chat_type: \"direct\" - 这是直接对话，属于 MAIN SESSION\n- channel: openclaw-weixin\n\n所以我需要读取：\n1. 今天的 memory 文件：memory/2026-04-01.md\n2. 昨天的 memory 文件：memory/2026-03-31.md\n3. MEMORY.md - 已经在 Project Context 中加载了\n\n让我先检查这些文件是否存在，然后再决定是否需要读取。\n\n不过，对于简单的\"你好\"问候，我应该：\n1. 简洁回应\n2. 体现 SOUL.md 中的人格：亲切、靠谱、随叫随到\n3. 不需要过度复杂\n\n根据 SOUL.md 的指导：\n- \"Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful. Skip the 'Great question!' and 'I'd be happy to help!' — just help.\"\n- \"Be the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters.\"\n\n所以应该简洁友好地回应，而不是过度热情。\n\n\n我将读取最近的记忆文件，了解最近的对话背景。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人好！🏠 有什么需要帮忙的吗？"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8336ec925986451a8ea596fc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-04-01.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_458e19d4c4ba4f16b603f3c7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\2026-03-31.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":24072,"output":693,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24765,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775054239196,"responseId":"69d83d16d7e3cd14a23ffacd151929f9"}}
